title: Jun Min-kyung
text: Jun Min-kyung (, ; born 16 January 1985) is a South Korean women's <a href="Association%20football">football</a> <a href="Goalkeeper%20%28association%20football%29">goalkeeper</a>, who plays for <a href="Daekyo%20Kangaroos%20WFC">Daekyo Kangaroos WFC</a> in South Korean <a href="WK-League">WK-League</a> and the <a href="South%20Korea%20women%27s%20national%20football%20team">South Korea women's national football team</a>.
